enough to worry about.

20:22.622 --> 20:23.823
Who's he?

20:23.856 --> 20:25.525
WOMAN: (OVER P.A.)
Attention shoppers.

20:25.558 --> 20:26.993
The store will be
closing in five minutes.

20:27.026 --> 20:30.597
Please bring all your
purchases to the front.
Thank you.

21:09.536 --> 21:10.670
Are you a slacker?

21:11.671 --> 21:14.841
Uh... No, uh, Presbyterian.

21:14.874 --> 21:17.076
What did you say?
What did you say?

21:17.109 --> 21:19.346
I'm askin' you
a simple question.

21:19.379 --> 21:21.548
Are you lazy?
No, sir.

21:21.581 --> 21:23.816
'Cause the last guy
that wore that uniform
was a lazy slacker,

21:23.850 --> 21:25.652
and I fired his no-good butt.

21:27.019 --> 21:29.789
Uh... About the uniform,

21:29.822 --> 21:31.491
