which I doubt,

21:33.893 --> 21:35.628
you can have
yourself a new name patch.

21:36.429 --> 21:37.430
(CHUCKLES)

21:40.733 --> 21:43.403
Eh, uh... Would I be
able to have it laundered?

21:43.436 --> 21:45.372
It smells a little bit
like Darnell. (CHUCKLES)

21:45.405 --> 21:48.375
I don't think you know
who you're messin' with, boy.

21:48.408 --> 21:50.777
Right, after you clean
the ladies' and
men's crappers,

21:50.810 --> 21:52.912
I'm talking about
you'd better be able
to eat off those bowls.

21:52.945 --> 21:54.781
Oh, sure.
You clean my coffeemaker,

21:54.814 --> 21:56.449
then you wax my desk.

21:56.483 --> 21:58.651
Uh, clean what?

21:58.685 --> 22:00.453
You clean my
coffeemaker and wax my desk!

22:00.487 --> 22:02.489
