24:05.878 --> 24:07.013
(LAUGHS) Boo!

24:07.046 --> 24:10.817
You can't do this.
I'm locked in,
alone, in the dark.

24:10.850 --> 24:12.852
That was not a part
of my employment agreement.

25:25.758 --> 25:26.793
Ah!

25:57.089 --> 25:58.825
