26:54.747 --> 26:56.716
(LAUGHING)

27:02.454 --> 27:03.923
Hello.

27:06.192 --> 27:07.860
Anybody out there?

27:07.894 --> 27:09.829
When I accepted the...

27:09.862 --> 27:13.032
The post of President,
grand Pooh-Bah of Target,

27:14.934 --> 27:17.336
realizing that I have brought

27:18.437 --> 27:20.940
meaningfulness and
peace and happiness,

27:20.973 --> 27:23.209
into the lives of
thousands of people.

27:24.010 --> 27:26.713
Jim Dodge, of Monroe,

27:26.746 --> 27:28.715
top moneymaker on the tour.

27:28.748 --> 27:31.117
His father's here today,
Bud Dodge,

27:31.150 --> 27:33.019
and sister Penny,
a sad, sad story,

27:33.052 --> 27:36.122
was just admitted to
university hospital.

27:36.155 --> 27:39.992
While trying to pop a zit,
her head
mysteriously exploded.

27:45.965 --> 27:47.734
