27:49.435 --> 27:51.003
(GROWLING)

27:51.904 --> 27:54.073
(SLURPING)

28:02.214 --> 28:04.316
(PHONE RINGING)

28:04.350 --> 28:06.085
JIM: Dad! Hi!

28:06.118 --> 28:08.020
Jim,
do you know what time it is?

28:08.054 --> 28:11.924
You know,
I'm starting to think
about Christmas and gifts,

28:11.958 --> 28:15.294
because I'm in a big store
and I'm starting to
get a lot of gift ideas.

28:15.327 --> 28:16.763
Hi.

28:16.796 --> 28:18.197
Mom, hi!

28:18.230 --> 28:20.166
How's it going?

28:20.199 --> 28:23.302
Well, I finished
all my janitor stuff,
I've finished most of it.

28:23.335 --> 28:25.204
I've got to save
some stuff for later.

28:25.237 --> 28:27.273
But it's easy as hell.

28:27.306 --> 28:30.042
Um, honey, it's a little late.

28:30.076 --> 28:33.112
Yeah, it is kind of late.
Well, sleep tight.

28:34.446 --> 28:36.482
See you in the morning.
(DIAL TONE)

28:36.515 --> 28:38.117
Love you, too.

28:43.355 --> 28:45.457
Mr. James Dodge!

29:41.380 --> 29:44.416
Oh. He can't be happy
as the night cleanup boy.

29:46.352 --> 29:48.087
Sweetheart...

29:49.055 --> 29:51.523
He wants us to
call him a janitor.

29:54.160 --> 29:58.330
Maybe I should have spent
less time harping
and more time helping.

29:59.298 --> 30:01.567
Harpin' and helpin' him what?

30:03.002 --> 30:07.139
Harpin' on him to leave,
and helpin' him become the...

30:07.173 --> 30:10.209
Good, mature,
productive person he could be.

31:31.390 --> 31:32.391
(GROANS)

31:40.399 --> 31:42.134
Are you all right?

31:43.735 --> 31:45.604
Yes, I'm fine, thanks.

31:45.637 --> 31:46.638
And you?

31:48.374 --> 31:49.675
What are you doing here?

31:51.410 --> 31:53.645
I work here.

31:53.679 --> 31:55.614
CARL:
Have a good one, Officer Don.

31:55.647 --> 31:59.585
Okay, Carl. Keep in touch.
Let me know if
you hear anything.

31:59.618 --> 32:01.220
CARL: You bet.

32:03.189 --> 32:05.424
Well, sir,
she didn't leave on the bus.

32:05.457 --> 32:08.594
Apparently, she isn't here.
Let's go look for
her someplace else.

32:08.627 --> 32:12.131
She wouldn't be dumb
enough to thumb, would she?

32:12.164 --> 32:15.534
Does she have any friends
that she might
have run off with?

32:16.235 --> 32:17.603
Boyfriends?

32:17.636 --> 32:21.407
Would you just get in the car
so we can go look
for the girl, please?

32:21.440 --> 32:23.442
I'm tired,
I had to get out of the bed,

32:23.475 --> 32:25.477
I haven't had any coffee.
I don't feel good.

32:25.511 --> 32:26.979
My daughter, I don't know
where the hell she is.

32:27.013 --> 32:28.580
And you're
standing by the car there,

32:28.614 --> 32:30.449
