goes on inside your heads.

01:08:36.813 --> 01:08:39.216
Okay, you had
the big one, you had the...

01:08:39.249 --> 01:08:40.750
No.

01:08:40.783 --> 01:08:42.419
Sorry. I could've
sworn you had the big one.

01:08:43.752 --> 01:08:45.488
Ha!

01:08:46.823 --> 01:08:48.792
