01:09:05.642 --> 01:09:08.345
Pretty darn close.
No.

01:09:08.377 --> 01:09:10.846
If I can get them
to take me with them,

01:09:10.880 --> 01:09:13.350
maybe I can get away
and come back for you.

01:09:13.383 --> 01:09:15.919
