and they obviously have one.

01:09:17.487 --> 01:09:19.389
Just...

01:09:19.423 --> 01:09:20.724
Go along with
whatever I do, okay?

01:09:20.756 --> 01:09:22.192
Okay.

01:09:34.537 --> 01:09:36.540
